- Fort Brimstone
	- mysterious origin
	- made desolate and bleak by the scourging
        - nothing grows in the area
            - (allegedly) uninhabited for this reason
    - massive stone fortress
    - its age is unknown
	- at the base of a small mountain (Mount [NAME])
		- mountain is a stubby, desolate plateau that is unmapped
		- given its temperature and lack of vegetation and water, it is argued that life of any kind cannot exist on it

	